item.title: Makati City So Far
item.description: Makati so far is 4 out of 4. We always see good food recommendations online and most of the time, it’s located in Makati. Here’s where we’ve been so far and it’s all 10/10. Mala Malatang Persian Samgyupsal New Bombay
